fields.title: SECOND ARTICLE
fields.content:
title = models.CharField(max_length=200, unique=True)
    slug = models.SlugField(help_text="Slugs are short versions of the title used for URLs")
    content = models.TextField()
    shortline = models.CharField(max_length=200, help_text="A short summary to show in the sidebar and under the article title")
    author = models.ForeignKey('Author', on_delete=models.SET_NULL, null=True)
    date_posted = models.DateTimeField(default=timezone.now)
    date_modified = models.DateTimeField(auto_now=True, editable=False)
    date_created = models.DateTimeField(auto_now_add=True)
    series = models.ForeignKey('Series', on_delete=models.SET_DEFAULT, default=0)
    tags = models.ManyToManyField('Tag')
    image = models.ImageField(upload_to="uploads/", blank=True)
    enabled = models.BooleanField(default=True)
fields.shortline: The second article to be hosted on the test site, this article also says nothing of note

fields.title: Welcome!
fields.content:
Welcome to my site!

I am John Clubb, and this page is my personal site. I use it to host certain projects: articles I write, projects I've worked on, etc. Many of the articles are simply about things that interest me, from linguistics to game design to things my friends say.

This site also doubles as a personal portfolio, as every aspect of it has been built by me from the ground up. I control the webserver directly, I installed and configured Nginx on it personally, I run email through it (which I also configured myself), the site runs through a Django project I built, and so and so forth. You can read more about the tool stack **HERE**.

This has been a labor of love long in the making, and I am very proud to have it live finally. Please feel free to check out any the pages here, read any of the articles, or check out my work. I also have some contact information at the bottom if you want to look me up that way. rabble rabble
fields.shortline: The site is finally live! Lots of hard work, and even more trial and error, has been put into bringing it to life.
